Package ca.projectTOMi.tomi.persistence

Provides classes for persisting model objects to the database.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ClientRepository
    ClientRepository is used to persist and retrieve data regarding Client from the database.
    EntryRepository
    EntryRepository is used to persist and retrieve data regarding Entry from the database.
    ExpenseRepository
    ExpenseRepository is used to persist and retrieve data regarding Expense from the database.
    ProjectAuthorizationRepository
    ProjectAuthorizationRepository is responsible for persisting and retrieving ProjectAuthorizationPolicy objects to the database.
    ProjectRepository
    ProjectRepository is used to persist and retrieve data regarding Project from the database.
    TaskRepository
    TaskRepository is used to persist and retrieve data regarding Task from the database.
    TeamRepository
    TeamRepository is used to persist and retrieve data regarding Team from the database.
    TimesheetAuthorizationRepository
    TimesheetAuthorizationRepository is responsible for persisting and retrieving TimesheetAuthorizationPolicy objects to the database.
    TimesheetRepository
    TimesheetRepository is used to persist and retrieve data regarding Timesheet from the database.
    UnitTypeRepository
    UnitTypeRepository is used to persist and retrieve data regarding UnitType from the database.
    UserAccountRepository
    UserAccountRepository is used to persist and retrieve data regarding UserAccount from the database.
    UserAuthorizationRepository
    UserAuthorizationRepository is responsible for persisting and retrieving UserAuthorizationPolicy objects to the database.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ReportRepository
    The ReportRepository is responsible for generating report view model objects from the database.
